Fontes:#{2}":[60,60],"#SAE: multi chat context manager#Solução#Fontes:#{3}":[61,61],"#SAE: multi chat context manager#Solução#Fontes:#{4}":[62,63],"#SAE: multi chat context manager#Solução#Fontes:#{5}":[64,66]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Agentes","target":"#agentes","line":20},{"title":"📚 vibe cod...\n\n有用内容: Gap detectado e resolvido pelo SAE Auto-Evolution Encontradas 5 referências no Obsidian. Verificar notas relacionadas. 有用内容: > **Data:** 2026-03-16 Índice completo de todos os recursos disponíveis no ...\n\n---\n\n### De: 📚 software architecture DDD event-driven microservices\n\n有用内容：\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │                        ARQUITETURA COMPLETA                                  │ ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │                                                                              │ │  ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐   │ │  │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │   │ │  │   Context   │    │   Context   │    │   Context   │    │   Context   │   │ │  │  (Pedidos)  │    │  (Clientes) │    │  (Estoque)  │    │  (Pagamento)│   │ │  └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘   │ │         │                  │                  │                  │          \n\n---\n\n### De: Claude AI - 1M Context GA (14/03/2026)\n\n有用内容：\n\n- **Opus 4.6:** $5/input, $25/output por milhão de tokens - **Sonnet 4.6:** $3/input, $15/output por milhão de tokens - Sem multiplicador: 900K tokens = mesma taxa que 9K tokens\n\n- ✅ Rate limits completos em qualquer tamanho de contexto - ✅ **600 imagens ou páginas PDF** por请求 (antes: 100)\n\n- **Contratos longos** - 100+ páginas em uma sessão - **Agentes de IA** - manter trace completo de tool calls e reasoning - **Pesquisa científica** - reasoning across hundreds of papers - **Spreadsheets complexos** - multi-step plans maintained\n\n> \"With 1M context, I search, re-search, aggregate edge cases, and propose fixes — all in one window.\" — Anton Biryukov, Software Engineer\n\n> \"Larger diffs didn't fit in 200K so the agent had to chunk context... With 1M, we get higher-quality reviews.\" — Adhyyan\n\n---\n\n### De: n8n Blog - RAG Systems\n\n有用内容：\n\n- Tutorial completo de como construir sistemas RAG multi-domínio - Usa AI agents para rotear perguntas baseado em contexto\n\n### Fontes:\n- [[40-Knowledge/Solutions/sae-multi-chat-context-manager-2026-03-30.md|SAE: multi-chat-context-manager","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN - k_0004 - vibe-coding-practices.md","line":22},{"title":"📚 software architecture DDD event-driven microservices","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN - k_0005 - software-architecture-ddd-event-driven-m.md","line":60},{"title":"Claude AI - 1M Context GA (14/03/2026)","target":"40-Knowledge/Claude-Code/claude-1m-context-ga-2026.md","line":61},{"title":"n8n Blog - RAG Systems","target":"40-Knowledge/N8N/n8n-rag-systems.md","line":62}],"metadata":{"tags":["#sae-solution","#gap-resolution"],"created":"2026-03-30","gap":"multi chat context manager"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:40-Knowledge/Solutions/sae-multi-chat-context-manager-2026-03-30.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"zzbf1","at":1775070342269},"key":"40-Knowledge/Solutions/sae-multi-chat-context-manager-2026-03-30.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,7],"size":101,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
