qualquer tamanho de contexto - ✅ **600 imagens ou páginas PDF** por请求 (antes: 100)\n\n- **Contratos longos** - 100+ páginas em uma sessão - **Agentes de IA** - manter trace completo de tool calls e reasoning - **Pesquisa científica** - reasoning across hundreds of papers - **Spreadsheets complexos** - multi-step plans maintained\n\n> \"With 1M context, I search, re-search, aggregate edge cases, and propose fixes — all in one window.\" — Anton Biryukov, Software Engineer\n\n> \"Larger diffs didn't fit in 200K so the agent had to chunk context... With 1M, we get higher-quality reviews.\" — Adhyyan\n\n---\n\n### De: n8n Blog - RAG Systems\n\n有用内容：\n\n- Tutorial completo de como construir sistemas RAG multi-domínio - Usa AI agents para rotear perguntas baseado em contexto\n\n### Fontes:\n- [[40-Knowledge/Solutions/sae-multi-chat-context-manager-2026-03-30.md|SAE: multi-chat-context-manager","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN - k_0004 - vibe-coding-practices.md","line":14},{"title":"📚 software architecture DDD event-driven microservices","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN - k_0005 - software-architecture-ddd-event-driven-m.md","line":52},{"title":"Claude AI - 1M Context GA (14/03/2026)","target":"40-Knowledge/Claude-Code/claude-1m-context-ga-2026.md","line":53},{"title":"n8n Blog - RAG Systems","target":"40-Knowledge/N8N/n8n-rag-systems.md","line":54}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
